---
<section>
    <div class="landing">
        <header>
            <div class="left">
                <h1>Â¿Que es contable?</h1>
                <p>
                    Es una herramienta en la cual te puedes apoyar para manejar tu contabilidad personal, con el fin de que en un futuro tengas un mejor control!!!
                </p>
                <div class="bottons">
                    <Button href="/auth/login" buttonText="Iniciar Sesion" />
                    <Button href="/auth/register" buttonText="Registrarse" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <footer>
            <figure>
                <img src="/Landing.png" alt="Contable Service">
            </figure>
        </footer>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    h1 {
        font-size: 50px;
        color: #393045;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    p {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #393045;
    }
    section {
        width: 100%;
        height: 747px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding-inline: 4rem;
    }
    .landing {
        width: 100%;
        height: 747px;
        background-color: white;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        border-radius: 30px;
        border: 1px rgba(126, 106, 151, 0.50) solid;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        display: inline-flex;
        min-width: 430px;
        @media (max-width: 1300px) {
            height: 700px;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
    }
    .left {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        padding-inline: 10%;
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    header {
        align-items: flex-start;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
    }
    footer {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        @media (max-width: 1300px){
            display: none;
        }
    }
    figure {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        @media (max-width: 1300px){
            display: none;
        }
    }
    img {
        width: 500px;
        height: 500px;
        @media (max-width: 1300px){
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
        }
    }
    .bottons {
        display: flex;
        height: 40px;
        gap: 2rem;
        @media (max-width: 1300px){
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>